data.description: REDUCED PRICE! Seller is offering some closing cost for full price offer to close within 30 days.  Updated Pictures! Welcome home to 1120 Madison! With well over 3000sqft, this spacious well-maintained home features 4 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms. Incredible master suite with sitting room and two walk-in closets! Updated lighting fixtures, fresh paint and newer carpets throughout the entire home. Luxury laminate flooring in updated kitchen and in all bathrooms with newer vanities! Tons of storage space in lower level. A new kitchen counter in home ready to install to stay. Come by and see the home for yourself, but be prepared to want to stay!
